snippet.title: The Coma 2B: Catacomb | Launch Trailer | Out Now!
snippet.description:
Youngho’s second adventure begins. With only the faint hope of escaping from the horrors within the mirror dimension, Youngho collects the pages of Yaesol’s notes to find the location of a powerful relic sword that can be used against the Vicious Sister.
